<li id="cite_note-Myth-49">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Myth_49-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Myth_49-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book"><i>The Myth of the Jewish Race</i>. Wayne State University Press. 1989. p.&#160;178. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0814319483" class="internal">ISBN 0814319483</a>, 9780814319482.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Myth+of+the+Jewish+Race&amp;rft.au=Raphael+and+Jennifer+Patai&amp;rft.date=1989&amp;rft.pages=p.%26nbsp%3B178&amp;rft.pub=Wayne+State+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0814319483%2C+9780814319482&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Antisemitism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-50"><b><a href="#cite_ref-50" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=4Iiw0KB31rgC&amp;pg=PA233&amp;ots=Se_CvAI3X6&amp;dq=Cracow+Kupa+synagogue+ritual+murder&amp;num=100&amp;sig=0t5WKlHjavg6aVgoL1ertcsPn9U" class="external autonumber" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=4Iiw0KB31rgC&amp;pg=PA233&amp;ots=Se_CvAI3X6&amp;dq=Cracow+Kupa+synagogue+ritual+murder&amp;num=100&amp;sig=0t5WKlHjavg6aVgoL1ertcsPn9U" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
