<li>Stav, Arieh (1999). <i>Peace: The Arabian Caricature - A Study of Anti-semitic Imagery</i>. Gefen Publishing House. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/965229215X" class="internal">ISBN 965-229-215-X</a></li>
