<li><a href="http://memri.org/" class="external text" title="http://memri.org/" rel="nofollow">The Middle East Media Research Institute</a> - documents antisemitism in Middle-Eastern media.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.zionism-israel.com/his/judeophobia.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.zionism-israel.com/his/judeophobia.htm" rel="nofollow">Judeophobia: A short course on the history of anti-Semitism</a> at <a href="http://www.zionism-israel.com" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.zionism-israel.com" rel="nofollow">[5]</a> Zionism and Israel Information Center.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pinteleyid.com" class="external text" title="http://www.pinteleyid.com" rel="nofollow">If Not Together, How?</a>: Research by April Rosenblum to develop a working definition of antisemitism, and related teaching tools about antisemitism, for activists.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.vintagepostcards.com/mm5/merchant.mvc?Screen=CTGY&amp;Category_Code=ethnjua" class="external text" title="http://www.vintagepostcards.com/mm5/merchant.mvc?Screen=CTGY&amp;Category_Code=ethnjua" rel="nofollow">Vintage Postcards with an Anti-Jewish theme</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/818365.html" class="external text" title="http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/818365.html" rel="nofollow">What makes an anti-Semite?</a> Dina Porat, <i>Haaretz</i>, January 27, 2007</li>
<li><a href="http://www.theaugeanstables.com/essays-on-judeophobia/anti-semitism-post-modern/" class="external text" title="http://www.theaugeanstables.com/essays-on-judeophobia/anti-semitism-post-modern/" rel="nofollow">"Post Modern"</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.theaugeanstables.com/2006/04/02/post-modern-anti-semitism-part-i/" class="external text" title="http://www.theaugeanstables.com/2006/04/02/post-modern-anti-semitism-part-i/" rel="nofollow">Post-Modern Anti-Semitism: Part I</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.theaugeanstables.com/reflections-from-second-draft/judeophobia-anti-judaism-anti-semitism-anti-zionism/" class="external text" title="http://www.theaugeanstables.com/reflections-from-second-draft/judeophobia-anti-judaism-anti-semitism-anti-zionism/" rel="nofollow">Judeophobia: Anti-Judaism, Anti-Semitism, Anti-Zionism</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.azure.org.il/article.php?id=18&amp;page=all" class="external text" title="http://www.azure.org.il/article.php?id=18&amp;page=all" rel="nofollow">An Attempt to Identify the Root Cause of Antisemitism</a> by <a href="/wiki/A.B._Yehoshua" title="A.B. Yehoshua" class="mw-redirect">A.B. Yehoshua</a>, <a href="http://www.azure.org.il" class="external text" title="http://www.azure.org.il" rel="nofollow">Azure</a>, Spring 2008.</li>
